            <p>
                <strong>2004-12-31</strong><br />
                The <a href="/download">first alpha version of phpMyFAQ 1.5.0</a> is ready.
                Besides a lot of code improvements this version adds support for PostgreSQL and Sybase databases,
                LDAP support and you can use mod_rewrite for search engine friendly URLs. Now you can link one FAQ
                record in various categories, the template engine can parse PHP code if you like, we have complete
                XML, XHTML and DocBook XML exports and a completely rewritten PDF export. Beside a better RSS support
                we've made a general code cleanup. Do not use this version in production systems, but test this version
                and report bugs!
            </p>
